## What we don't look like (AI-slop fingerprints — avoid)

- Gradient backgrounds
- Glow / glassmorphism effects
- Centered hero text with a decorative subtitle
- Card grids where every card has a drop shadow
- Emoji in button labels or headings
- "Comfortable" padding that doesn't follow the spacing scale

