## Process gate

1. Enter Plan Mode before any visual work.
2. State: "I'm going to implement {screen}. The aesthetic goal is {brief}. The states are {list}."
3. Approve the state brief.
4. Implement.
5. Screenshot at 1440px + 390px. Compare against this brief.
6. Fix divergences in plain English, then re-screenshot.
